description:
BIC® Hybrid 3 Comfort? is a disposable razor handle with 12 cartridges. When you have used all of the cartridges, simply dispose of the handle and purchase a new package. BIC® Hybrid 3 Comfort? provides triple blade closeness and a pivoting head allows for a comfortable shave. The lubricating strip with Aloe & Vitamin E provides a smooth glide.

- 3 blades provide a close, comfortable shave
- Ergonomic handle and pivoting head for better control as you shave
- Enhanced lubricating strip for extra glide
- A new handle and 12 cartridges in every packaged provides added convenience
name: Bic Hybrid 3 Comfort Shaver 12 Pack
